//PS:GET=获取，查询 POST＝新增 DELETE＝删除  PUT＝更新            
患者档案 
 /persons/{id} 
GET  /persons/{id} 获取患者档案 
POST /persons      新增患者档案 
DELETE  /persons/{id} 删除患者档案
PUT  /persons/{id} 更新患者档案
－病史
/conditions
GET  /persons/{id}/conditions
POST /persons/{id}/conditions
DELETE /persons/{id}/conditions/{condition_id}
PUT /persons/{id}/conditions/{condition_id}

	